15:49.239 --> 15:52.201
You're ugly.

15:54.244 --> 15:56.830
Idiot! What's he doing?

15:57.206 --> 15:59.083
Hey, they're leaving!

16:02.544 --> 16:03.879
I LOVE YOU. BE MINE.

16:04.004 --> 16:07.925
What is this? Get out of my face!

16:08.050 --> 16:09.134
What's wrong?

16:09.259 --> 16:13.681
I want to be with you

16:14.556 --> 16:18.852
Hold me in your arms

16:21.021 --> 16:22.773
Bye, now.

16:24.525 --> 16:28.862
- No, let's go for another round.
- Sure!

16:28.988 --> 16:30.781
What the hell?
Do everything we prepared!

16:45.587 --> 16:48.424
FIRST DATE

16:49.341 --> 16:52.428
I'm having my first date with Ae-bong.
Can I really do it?

16:52.553 --> 16:55.806
Don't worry! Anyone can do it.

16:55.931 --> 16:57.766
If you can't, you're a pathetic moron.

16:57.891 --> 17:00.144
But it's my first date ever.

17:00.602 --> 17:01.729
There's nothing much to it.

17:01.854 --> 17:04.189
- First, you eat.
- Eat?

17:06.150 --> 17:09.945
Now, we've eaten together.
Shall we get married?

17:10.612 --> 17:11.488
Yes.

17:15.159 --> 17:18.037
What? Straight to marriage?

17:18.162 --> 17:21.081
- Eat and then go to a movie or something!
- A movie?

17:33.218 --> 17:35.179
Marriage, again? Why?

17:35.304 --> 17:36.805
You must proceed step by step!

17:36.930 --> 17:41.018
Take a walk and hold her hand naturally.

17:41.643 --> 17:42.978
Hold her hand?

17:49.651 --> 17:52.404
- Good job!
- You, too.

17:54.239 --> 17:56.825
How could you cheat on me?

17:56.950 --> 17:58.911
Every man makes mistakes.

17:59.036 --> 18:00.287
- Go to your room, and keep crying.
- Sorry.

18:00.412 --> 18:02.331
It's time to watch the news. Run!

18:03.082 --> 18:05.292
- Father!
- Don't call me "father"!

18:05.417 --> 18:07.377
You can't marry my daughter!

18:08.337 --> 18:10.089
SEOK CHO
1988-2077

18:10.214 --> 18:12.424
Goodbye, honey.

18:12.883 --> 18:15.761
Oh, what a pathetic moron!

18:17.679 --> 18:22.476
Hmm, first date. Isn't it simple?

18:22.601 --> 18:25.729
As far as I know, you go to a movie,

18:25.854 --> 18:27.106
you walk and hold hands.

18:27.731 --> 18:30.526
- Right?
- Right.

18:31.110 --> 18:32.986
