Oh, Seok,
I'm sorry for punching you so hard.

19:03.308 --> 19:06.603
Oh, my God!
She knows nothing about romance!

19:06.728 --> 19:08.397
You're hopeless.

19:08.522 --> 19:10.274
If you fail again,

19:10.399 --> 19:13.068
- we'll ask a great wizard.
- A great wizard?

19:13.193 --> 19:16.155
Don't worry. We'll ask everyone
who knows all about romance.

19:16.280 --> 19:17.865
- Trust us.
- Trust.

19:17.990 --> 19:21.577
If you acquire their skills,
you can become a Don Juan.

