22:47.908 --> 22:50.327
Mouse!

22:50.577 --> 22:53.580
Mouse!

22:53.705 --> 22:58.085
Run! A mouse!

22:59.127 --> 22:59.961
Come here.

23:01.505 --> 23:04.966
From today, your name is Minky.

23:05.092 --> 23:06.343
Minky!

23:07.886 --> 23:09.304
She's so cute!

23:14.392 --> 23:17.813
SKILL: WHEN SHE SPEAKS ILL
OF SOMEONE, CHIME IN WITH HER

23:17.938 --> 23:21.316
How dare she talk to me like that?

23:21.441 --> 23:24.903
Oh, she's a bitch!

23:25.028 --> 23:25.946
Isn't she?

23:26.488 --> 23:29.241
I've recently gained weight.
I look so fat.

23:29.366 --> 23:32.077
Right, you do look fat.

23:34.204 --> 23:36.915
I tried to make her feel better,
so I talked to my mom.

23:37.040 --> 23:38.708
But all of a sudden, she got mad.

23:38.834 --> 23:41.628
You mom is so bad!

23:48.218 --> 23:52.222
APPLIED SKILL:
SAY YOU LOVE WHAT SHE LOVES

23:52.347 --> 23:55.308
I love going to a bathhouse with my mom.

23:55.475 --> 23:57.894
Oh, me, too.
I love going to a bathhouse with my mom.

23:59.229 --> 24:02.023
In winter, skirt leggings are the best!

24:02.149 --> 24:05.318
Me, too. I wear them in winter!

24:07.779 --> 24:09.239
Well, actually I love Exo and Xiumin!

24:11.199 --> 24:12.951
Me, too. I love Exo and Xiumin!

24:13.535 --> 24:14.619
THIS IS TRUE!

24:14.995 --> 24:16.454
Roar, roar, roar!

24:16.580 --> 24:18.081
D.O., BAEKHYUN, KAI, SEHUN

24:18.206 --> 24:21.168
Take this water!

24:26.423 --> 24:29.342
SKILL: BE NICE TO PEOPLE AROUND YOU

24:29.467 --> 24:31.136
You're doing such a great job.

24:31.261 --> 24:34.472
Oh, your hands are so dry. Wait.

24:47.694 --> 24:49.154
Oh, you walk around a lot.
your legs must be tired.

24:49.279 --> 24:51.573
- Sit here.
- No, thanks.

24:58.163 --> 25:02.542
SKILL: BE NICE TO CHILDREN

25:02.667 --> 25:07.297
Oh, how old are you?

25:07.422 --> 25:08.840
Where is your mom?

25:09.925 --> 25:11.092
Oh, is she your mom?

25:13.887 --> 25:17.098
Oh, it must be really hard
to take your grandson with you.

25:17.224 --> 25:18.600
Can I help you with anything?

25:19.059 --> 25:20.477
$2.50.

25:20.602 --> 25:22.187
$2.50.

25:27.025 --> 25:27.984
- $2.50.
- $2.50.

25:29.486 --> 25:35.116
Oh, I don't have cash!
I have credit cards.

25:37.661 --> 25:40.288
Oh, I was wrong.

25:40.497 --> 25:42.791
I have cashier's checks, not credit cards.

25:42.916 --> 25:45.001
If you can give me change...

25:45.752 --> 25:47.796
in dollars.
No, in yen.

25:53.760 --> 25:55.637
They have all that money.
Why do they sell gum?

25:55.762 --> 25:56.805
Exactly.

26:01.059 --> 26:02.185
- Let's drink.
- Yeah.

26:02.686 --> 26:04.938
Cheers!

26:06.982 --> 26:12.612
Oh, I'm drunk.

26:12.737 --> 26:16.908
So, my parents went on a trip
by themselves.

26:17.033 --> 26:20.620
They're not home tonight.

26:24.291 --> 26:26.960
SKILL: JUST BE A MAN
SOURCE: XY CHROMOSOMES

26:27.085 --> 26:30.630
Why don't we finish this off,
and go to my house for the second round?

26:33.675 --> 26:37.470
- Yeah.
- For the second round!

26:40.640 --> 26:42.350
Taxi, taxi!

26:45.145 --> 26:47.272
- Hi, get in.
- Hi.

26:47.731 --> 26:51.234
Ae-bong, tell me your address.

26:52.902 --> 26:58.867
Gamcheon-dong, Saha-gu, Busan.

26:59.909 --> 27:01.494
Busan? Okay!

27:01.745 --> 27:02.579
Well--

27:09.085 --> 27:10.337
$160

27:17.344 --> 27:18.970
$250

27:25.852 --> 27:27.437
Can I pay by credit card?

27:43.912 --> 27:45.038
Come on in.

27:47.582 --> 27:48.625
Shall I?

27:59.177 --> 28:00.970
This is my house.

28:09.896 --> 28:12.023
Hey, say hello to my grandma.

28:14.317 --> 28:15.860
Here's my grandpa.

28:15.985 --> 28:18.363
- Hi, sis.
- That's my brother.

28:19.906 --> 28:22.242
My aunt and uncle.

28:23.785 --> 28:25.036
Another uncle.

28:26.621 --> 28:29.165
The big one is Sensation.

28:29.290 --> 28:30.875
And the little one is Snow White.

28:32.836 --> 28:36.631
Did I mention
my parents went on a trip?

28:38.007 --> 28:40.427
Yes, you did.

28:44.180 --> 28:49.018
WHAT ABOUT THE SECOND ROUND?

28:55.734 --> 28:57.777
Cheers! Wave!

28:58.862 --> 29:00.530
Drink, drink up!

29:02.490 --> 29:03.700
One more time!

29:03.825 --> 29:05.493
Cheers!

29:08.538 --> 29:12.083
One more time!
One more time!

29:12.208 --> 29:15.086
- Cross the bridge!
- One more time!

29:15.211 --> 29:16.337
Let's give a shout!

29:16.463 --> 29:21.509
- They're inferior to dogs!
- I don't want to be with these morons!

29:21.634 --> 29:24.471
Who's the ugly guy?

29:24.596 --> 29:27.766
Ae-bong's boyfriend.
He came here all the way from Seoul.

29:27.891 --> 29:32.228
Ae-bong must've said
her parents weren't home.

29:32.353 --> 29:34.898
Oh, that poor thing!

29:35.023 --> 29:39.360
I called her.

29:41.154 --> 29:43.281
Oh, shit...!
